          "fill": "#92400E",
          "content": "📌 NAVIGATION — Live Identification",
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 14,
          "fontWeight": "700"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "SCwOu",
          "name": "navBody",
          "fill": "#78350F",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "content": "[jDuTA] ← Back → xEPrW Photo Menu or Ij4bQ Gallery Grid\n[Q7yXT] 🎙 Push-to-talk mic → Gemini Live Agent confirms/rejects via voice\n  User says \"yes\" → vE9pj Artwork Analysis (confirmed)\n  User says \"no\" / corrects → AI retries or asks for name\n  User provides name → vE9pj (user-provided title)\n[4h5h9] \"Or type it myself\" → text input fallback → vE9pj\n\nLIVE AGENT FLOW:\n  AI speaks: \"I think this is The Hay Wain by John Constable...\"\n  User responds naturally via voice (interruptible)\n  AI confirms, corrects, or asks follow-up\n\nEntry: after camera capture from xEPrW / p39d7\nEntry: tap unconfirmed artwork card in Ij4bQ Gallery Grid\nMerge: if photo matches existing artwork → merge into same vE9pj",
          "lineHeight": 1.6,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 12,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        }
      ]
    }
